Key Responsibilities:
 Travels a predefined courier route via automobile to deliver mail and parcels throughout the campus. 
Keeps log and time stamp of items received and delivered. 
Supports chain of custody requirements defined within the operating procedures. 
Performs pick-up and delivery of jobs by accurately following a map and/or written instructions. 
Follows Operational Service Excellence performance requirements. 
Responds to client requests, ensuring the accuracy of the order taken and delivery of the completed orders in a timely manner. 
Completes all paperwork in a timely, accurate and legible manner. 
Responsible for maintaining compliance with state and company standards by operating a vehicle in a safe and lawful manner and following company guidelines in the event of an accident and/or injury. 
Presents professional appearance to clients by dressing in professional attire according to company standards. 
Responsible for vehicle safety by maintaining routine maintenance on all delivery vehicles (oil change, tire rotation, etc.) according to company specifications. 
Services vehicle driven, such as checking fluid levels and replenishing fuel. 
Delivers mail and parcels throughout the campus. 
Performs pick-up and delivery. 
Responds to client requests accurately and in a timely manner. 
Services the vehicle driven. 
Competencies : 
Strong verbal and written communication skills 
Excellent customer service skills 
Excellent driving record 
Good organizational skills 
Qualifications: 
Requires high school diploma 
Must be flexible to work hours between 7:00 am and 6:00 pm (full time â€“ 8 hour shifts) 
Physical Demands: 
Fine and/or gross motor skills, including the ability to grasp, lift and/or carry or otherwise move packages on a standard wheeled cart with a load capacity of 60 lbs. 
Ability to walk, bend, kneel, stand, and/or sit for an extended period of time. 
Manual dexterity required for operating office machinery (phone, copy machines, binding equipment, etc.) 
Ability to lift or move 40 lbs. or greater frequently 
Travel: Local travel required 
